<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> matsyānvavāyā bahavaḥ pūrvamāsanmahībhujaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tēṣāṁ bhāgavataḥ śrīmānprahlāda Iva satpriya<unclear>ḥ</unclear> [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*]
<lb n="2"/>jayaṁta Iti rājāsītpratyartthimadabhaṁjanaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasyā<unclear>sī</unclear>darjjunō nāma tanayaḥ kṣōṇināyakaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> śrīkṛṣṇavarddha
<lb n="3" break="no"/>na Iti khyātastasyāpi bhūbhujaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> jayaṁta nāmā nṛpati<unclear>rjja</unclear>yaṁttasamavikramaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> rūpaudāryyayaśōvīryya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dhairyyaśrīkīrttisaṁyutaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nṛsiṁhacaraṇē bhakta<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> svābhīṣṭaphalasiddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> [sudhāṁśurasadṛk bhūmi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>gaṇitē śakavatsarē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mārggaśīrṣāccha saptamyāṁ śōbhanē sōmavāsarē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">5</supplied> sa pratyahaṁ pakvadudhgasannivē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>danasiddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> savatsaṁ gōśataṁ prādānnṛharēssumanoharaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ācaṁdrārkkamimaṁ dha<unclear>rmmaṁ</unclear> pālayaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tviha vaiṣṇavāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">6</supplied> śakavarṣaṁbhulu 1261 gunē<unclear>ṭi</unclear> mārggaśira śukla saptamiyu sōmavāramunāṁḍu
<lb n="8"/>Oḍḍavādi jayaṁtarāju tanaku Āyurārōgyaiśvaryyaputravijayābhivṛddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dhunika pratidinemunnu Adhdhavaddu pālāragiṁppapeṭṭina mōdālu 100 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī mōdālu māvāli gōcaramu pri
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Ī dharmmu Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigā śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa śrī śrī
